INSERT INTO `ai_gpt_chat_message` VALUES (78456528373500945, 78456528373500943, 'chatcmpl-67ca5f6fd44f088c134f28a3', 'c748bc9e-3f32-4d81-8393-6e125da370fc', 'Moonshot', 'moonshot-v1-8k', '好的，我将为你设计一个基于Python和selenium库的双十一自动抢购脚本。这个脚本将使用面向对象编程方式，实现自动登录购物网站和定时抢购预设商品的功能。\n\n首先，你需要确保已经安装了Python和selenium库。如果没有安装，可以通过以下命令安装：\n\n```bash\npip install selenium\n```\n\n接下来，你需要下载对应浏览器的WebDriver，例如ChromeDriver或GeckoDriver，并将其路径添加到系统环境变量中。\n\n以下是双十一自动抢购脚本的代码：\n\n```python\nfrom selenium import webdriver\nfrom selenium.webdriver.common.by import By\nfrom selenium.webdriver.common.keys import Keys\nfrom selenium.webdriver.support.ui import WebDriverWait\nfrom selenium.webdriver.support import expected_conditions as EC\nimport time\n\nclass AutoBuyer:\n    def __init__(self, username, password, target_url, target_product_url, buy_time):\n        self.username = username\n        self.password = password\n        self.target_url = target_url\n        self.target_product_url = target_product_url\n        self.buy_time = buy_time\n        self.driver = webdriver.Chrome()\n\n    def login(self):\n        self.driver.get(self.target_url)\n        time.sleep(2)\n        \n        username_input = self.driver.find_element(By.ID, \'loginname\')\n        password_input = self.driver.find_element(By.ID, \'nloginpwd\')\n        login_button = self.driver.find_element(By.ID, \'loginsubmit\')\n        \n        username_input.send_keys(self.username)\n        password_input.send_keys(self.password)\n        login_button.click()\n        time.sleep(2)\n\n    def navigate_to_product(self):\n        self.driver.get(self.target_product_url)\n        time.sleep(2)\n\n    def buy_product(self):\n        buy_button = WebDriverWait(self.driver, 10).until(\n            EC.element_to_be_clickable((By.XPATH, \'//button[@class=\"buy-button\"]\'))\n        )\n        buy_button.click()\n        time.sleep(2)\n\n    def close_browser(self):\n        self.driver.quit()\n\n    def run(self):\n        while True:\n            current_time = time.strftime(\'%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\', time.localtime(time.time()))\n            if current_time >= self.buy_time:\n                self.login()\n                self.navigate_to_product()\n                self.buy_product()\n                self.close_browser()\n                break\n            else:\n                time.sleep(60)\n\nif __name__ == \'__main__\':\n    username = \'your_username\'\n    password = \'your_password\'\n    target_url = \'https://www.example.com/login\'\n    target_product_url = \'https://www.example.com/product\'\n    buy_time = \'2023-11-11 00:00:00\'\n\n    auto_buyer = AutoBuyer(username, password, target_url, target_product_url, buy_time)\n    auto_buyer.run()\n```\n\n这个脚本的主要功能如下：\n\n1. `AutoBuyer` 类：封装了自动登录、导航到商品页面、购买商品和关闭浏览器的方法。\n2. `__init__` 方法：初始化类的实例，包括用户名、密码、目标URL、商品URL和购买时间。\n3. `login` 方法：自动登录购物网站。\n4. `navigate_to_product` 方法：导航到预设商品的页面。\n5. `buy_product` 方法：点击购买按钮，完成购买操作。\n6. `close_browser` 方法：关闭浏览器。\n7. `run` 方法：循环检查当前时间，当达到购买时间时，执行登录、导航和购买操作。\n\n请根据你的实际需求，替换脚本中的用户名、密码、目标URL和商品URL。希望这个脚本能帮助你在双十一当天自动抢购心仪的商品！', 'text', 'assistant', 'stop', 2, '', 0, NULL, '', 3, '2025-03-07 10:52:51', NULL, NULL, 0);
