INSERT INTO `ai_gpt_chat_message` VALUES (78911494259207230, 78911494259207228, 'chatcmpl-67cc0c9214278be9fbb39fae', '59a41e1f-7393-4a54-ad46-624017432e3e', 'Moonshot', 'moonshot-v1-8k', '好的，我将为你设计一个基于Python和selenium库的双十一自动抢购脚本。这个脚本将使用面向对象编程方式，实现自动登录购物网站和定时抢购预设商品的功能。\n\n首先，你需要确保已经安装了Python和selenium库。如果没有安装，可以通过以下命令安装：\n\n```bash\npip install selenium\n```\n\n接下来，你需要下载对应浏览器的WebDriver，例如ChromeDriver或GeckoDriver，并将其路径添加到系统环境变量中。\n\n以下是双十一自动抢购脚本的代码：\n\n```python\nfrom selenium import webdriver\nfrom selenium.webdriver.common.by import By\nfrom selenium.webdriver.common.keys import Keys\nfrom selenium.webdriver.support.ui import WebDriverWait\nfrom selenium.webdriver.support import expected_conditions as EC\nimport time\n\nclass AutoBuyer:\n    def __init__(self, username, password, target_url, target_product_url, buy_time):\n        self.username = username\n        self.password = password\n        self.target_url = target_url\n        self.target_product_url = target_product_url\n        self.buy_time = buy_time\n        self.driver = webdriver.Chrome()\n\n    def login(self):\n        self.driver.get(self.target_url)\n        time.sleep(3)  # 等待页面加载\n\n        # 输入用户名和密码\n        username_input = self.driver.find_element(By.ID, \"username\")\n        password_input = self.driver.find_element(By.ID, \"password\")\n        username_input.send_keys(self.username)\n        password_input.send_keys(self.password)\n\n        # 点击登录按钮\n        login_button = self.driver.find_element(By.ID, \"login\")\n        login_button.click()\n        time.sleep(3)  # 等待登录成功\n\n    def buy_product(self):\n        self.driver.get(self.target_product_url)\n        time.sleep(3)  # 等待页面加载\n\n        # 点击立即购买按钮\n        buy_button = self.driver.find_element(By.ID, \"buy\")\n        buy_button.click()\n        time.sleep(3)  # 等待跳转到结算页面\n\n        # 点击提交订单按钮\n        submit_button = self.driver.find_element(By.ID, \"submit\")\n        submit_button.click()\n        time.sleep(3)  # 等待订单提交成功\n\n    def run(self):\n        self.login()\n        time.sleep(10)  # 等待到抢购时间\n\n        # 循环抢购商品\n        while True:\n            current_time = time.strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\", time.localtime())\n            if current_time >= self.buy_time:\n                self.buy_product()\n                break\n            time.sleep(60)  # 每分钟检查一次时间\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    username = \"your_username\"\n    password = \"your_password\"\n    target_url = \"https://www.example.com/login\"\n    target_product_url = \"https://www.example.com/product\"\n    buy_time = \"2023-11-11 00:00:00\"\n\n    auto_buyer = AutoBuyer(username, password, target_url, target_product_url, buy_time)\n    auto_buyer.run()\n```\n\n这个脚本的主要功能如下：\n\n1. `AutoBuyer` 类：用于自动登录和抢购商品。\n2. `__init__` 方法：初始化用户名、密码、目标URL、目标商品URL和抢购时间。\n3. `login` 方法：自动登录购物网站。\n4. `buy_product` 方法：自动抢购预设商品。\n5. `run` 方法：运行抢购脚本，等待到抢购时间后执行抢购操作。\n\n你可以根据实际需求修改用户名、密码、目标URL和抢购时间等参数。希望这个脚本能帮助你实现双十一自动抢购的需求。', 'text', 'assistant', 'stop', 2, '', 0, NULL, '', 3, '2025-03-08 17:23:55', NULL, NULL, 0);
